{
  "stem": "13673.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And she called the police station, and they had taken, taken him there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "My uncle next door was there, too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And from there, they had taken him to Dachau.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think so, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, perhaps she did know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I, I-- at that time, I knew it was a concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I don't think so.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, we never really did.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not to my old school, no.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a-- I guess a few days went by, and then the-- and then I was sent to a Jewish school.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "These Jewish schools were open, schools were opened up immediately so that the children could go on going to school.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Jewish community was well organized.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I guess, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All I remember-- and it was only a few months that I was going there anyway.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What I remember, it was November, so Hanukkah was coming up, and I learned about Hanukkah.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I never knew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when I came home to tell my mother about it-- because at that point, everybody was gone.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My, my maid, Frieda, was no longer with us because she wasn't-- I'm getting to Hanukkah-- because she, she wasn't allowed by, by the Nuremberg laws to work for us anymore.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Rationale?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, well, any young, so-called Aryan woman under a certain age-- let's make it 35.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm not, I'm not positive about that-- couldn't work for Jewish people anymore probably-- I don't know, the Jewish people were going to do something dreadful to them.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Anyway.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, and my brother was already in England in school at that time, and now my father was gone.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it was just my mother and I.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I came home and told her about Hanukkah.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
